Our deployments managers exhibit a rare combination of deep technical expertise and exceptional emotional intelligence. Our perfect candidate obsesses over building and optimizing, has the technical chops to dive into any data problem, and loves tackling complex product issues. They thrive working directly with our clients, and can clearly communicate their frontline knowledge to our product teams, while playing an instrumental role in building new tools to scale our process.</p>
<p>
<br />
We expect members of our deployment team to have a deep understanding of finance. You&rsquo;ll be interacting with the front and back offices of the world&rsquo;s most sophisticated advisers and investors, but at the same time will be in constant contact with some of the best technologists and engineers in Silicon Valley. Deployment team members are required to exist and thrive in both worlds.</p>
<p>
<br />
<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Work closely with clients to deploy the Addepar platform and ensure our deployed product exceeds their expectations</li>
<li>
Clearly and effectively set and manage expectations</li>
<li>
Work closely with product, engineering and data teams</li>
<li>
Manage the data onboarding process for new clients while leveraging technical expertise to migrate data on to Addepar</li>
<li>
Continue to develop and refine the tools to make our deployments turnkey and as seamless as possible</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Degree in CS, Math, or related Engineering Field</li>
<li>
1-3 years of previous experience in finance</li>
<li>
Working knowledge of scripting languages, i.e. python, perl, ruby</li>
<li>
Solid understanding of asset allocation and performance metrics</li>
<li>
Strong communication skills and the ability to understand clients&rsquo; business needs</li>
<li>
Passionate about technology and software development</li>
<li>
Unstoppable work ethic and motivation</li>
<li>
{Bonus} Deep understanding of wealth management industry</li>
</ul>
